                <div2> weekly schedule /// ### Sunshine Kindergarten Weekly Schedule
                    **Monday**  
                    - **8:30 AM - 9:00 AM:** Morning Arrival & Free Play  
                    - **9:00 AM - 9:30 AM:** Circle Time (Songs & Stories)  
                    - **9:30 AM - 10:15 AM:** Art Exploration (Painting & Crafting)  
                    - **10:15 AM - 10:30 AM:** Snack Time  
                    - **10:30 AM - 11:15 AM:** Outdoor Play (Gardening & Nature Walk)  
                    - **11:15 AM - 12:00 PM:** Learning Centers (Math & Science Activities)  
                    - **12:00 PM - 12:30 PM:** Lunch  
                    - **12:30 PM - 1:00 PM:** Quiet Reading Time  
                    - **1:00 PM - 1:30 PM:** Music & Movement  
                    - **1:30 PM - 2:00 PM:** Closing Circle (Reflections of the Day)  
                    ---
                    **Tuesday**  
                    - **8:30 AM - 9:00 AM:** Morning Arrival & Free Play  
                    - **9:00 AM - 9:30 AM:** Circle Time (Discussion & Sharing)  
                    - **9:30 AM - 10:15 AM:** Storytime & Dramatic Play  
                    - **10:15 AM - 10:30 AM:** Snack Time  
                    - **10:30 AM - 11:15 AM:** STEM Exploration (Building & Experiments)  
                    - **11:15 AM - 12:00 PM:** Outdoor Games  
                    - **12:00 PM - 12:30 PM:** Lunch  
                    - **12:30 PM - 1:00 PM:** Art & Sensory Play  
                    - **1:00 PM - 1:30 PM:** Language & Literacy Activities  
                    - **1:30 PM - 2:00 PM:** Closing Circle  
                    ---
                    **Wednesday**  
                    - **8:30 AM - 9:00 AM:** Morning Arrival & Free Play  
                    - **9:00 AM - 9:30 AM:** Circle Time (Theme of the Week)  
                    - **9:30 AM - 10:15 AM:** Science Exploration (Nature & Animals)  
                    - **10:15 AM - 10:30 AM:** Snack Time  
                    - **10:30 AM - 11:15 AM:** Creative Movement (Dance & Yoga)  
                    - **11:15 AM - 12:00 PM:** Group Games  
                    - **12:00 PM - 12:30 PM:** Lunch  
                    - **12:30 PM - 1:00 PM:** Free Choice Activities  
                    - **1:00 PM - 1:30 PM:** Technology Time (Age-Appropriate Apps)  
                    - **1:30 PM - 2:00 PM:** Closing Circle  
                    ---
                    **Thursday**  
                    - **8:30 AM - 9:00 AM:** Morning Arrival & Free Play  
                    - **9:00 AM - 9:30 AM:** Circle Time (Weather & Calendar)  
                    - **9:30 AM - 10:15 AM:** Cooking & Healthy Eating  
                    - **10:15 AM - 10:30 AM:** Snack Time  
                    - **10:30 AM - 11:15 AM:** Math Games (Counting & Shapes)  
                    - **11:15 AM - 12:00 PM:** Outdoor Play (Playground & Sports)  
                    - **12:00 PM - 12:30 PM:** Lunch  
