                    - **1:00 PM - 1:30 PM:** Art & Crafting  
                    - **1:30 PM - 2:00 PM:** Closing Circle  
                    ---
                    **Friday**  
                    - **8:30 AM - 9:00 AM:** Morning Arrival & Free Play  
                    - **9:00 AM - 9:30 AM:** Circle Time (Feelings & Friendship)  
                    - **9:30 AM - 10:15 AM:** Field Trip or Special Guest  
                    - **10:15 AM - 10:30 AM:** Snack Time  
                    - **10:30 AM - 11:15 AM:** Group Projects (Collaboration Activities)  
                    - **11:15 AM - 12:00 PM:** Outdoor Exploration  
                    - **12:00 PM - 12:30 PM:** Lunch  
                    - **12:30 PM - 1:00 PM:** Reflection & Sharing  
                    - **1:00 PM - 1:30 PM:** Fun Friday Games  
                    - **1:30 PM - 2:00 PM:** Closing Circle & Goodbye  
                    ---
                    **Note:** This schedule can be adjusted based on the needs and interests of the children. We aim to create a flexible and engaging environment that promotes learning through play! </div2> <br>

